                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Parce que je n'ai plus de sourire joyeux",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Parce que, de l'amour me faisant un linceul,",
